Company Description:
HCA West Florida is a comprehensive network of hospitals, outpatient surgery and diagnostic imaging facilities, physician practices, medical education and training programs and a complete continuum of specialized health programs and services that meet the healthcare needs of residents and businesses in West Florida communities.

In 2014, we treated more than 1.1 million patients. Our parent company, HCA, is the nation’s leading provider of healthcare services. HCA West Florida affiliated facilities include:

16 hospitals on 18 Campuses;
12 ambulatory surgery centers;
diagnostic imaging facilities and occupational health sites;
an integrated regional lab;
and a consolidated service center.

Make excellence your goal by joining our family of hospitals. To learn more, please visit us at www.MoreCareerChoices.com.

Abacustel Communications, Inc. <www.abacustel.net> provides communication solutions to small & medium businesses in South Florida since 2007.

Through experienced and certified staff, and supported by strong partnerships with Technological leaders (Cisco, Ruckus Wireless, Nomadix, SonicWall, ...), and other Service Providers (Windstream, RingCentral, ...), we provide to SMB companies a complete array of solutions including but not limited to

   - unified communications (voice, data, wireless, video conference, security, mobility);
   - hosted PBX (Phone Systems);
   - smart wireless networks for small and medium developments (up to 1,000 users);
   - local & long distance telephone services;
   - competed broadband Internet (wired and wireless);
   - structured cabling (voice, data, surveillance, video);

From an evaluation of your current communication technology in use up to the development and implementation of a complete solution, including the training of its employees and the change of services, Abacustel Communications can be your trusted partner.
